    "These messages consist of two key-value pairs:",
    "Role: Identifies the sender of the message, which can be: 2.",
    "System: Sets the assistant's behavior and has priority over user instructions. 3.",
    "Assistant: Signifies the AI model interacting with the user. 4.",
    "User: Denotes the person communicating with the assistant (in this case, the student). 5."
